com.documentum.operations

Interface IDfNodePopulatorContext


  • public interface IDfNodePopulatorContext
    This interface provides access to other interfaces that can be used for creating or building a node tree. It provides a depdendency injection mechanism for populators.
    Since:
    7.0
    See Also:
    IDfNodePopulator

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      IDfOperationNodeFactory getNodeFactory()
      Returns a factory that can create IDfOperationNode objects
      IDfOperationNodeTreeBuilder getNodeTreeBuilder()
      Returns an object that is responsible for building a node tree.
